In the 1990s, some of the most iconic arcade games — from Mortal Kombat to NBA Jam — were created by a Chicago company called Midway Games. 

The documentary “Insert Coin” looks back at the company’s heyday and is available to stream through Dec. 10 https://t.co/pCqB4sLHLT
